Changelog
=========
[A] = Added new feature
[B] = Bugfix (fix something that wasn't working as expected)
[C] = Cosmetical fix (layout, typo etc.)
[D] = Documentation improvements
[M] = Maintenance works
[O] = Optimization of code
[S] = Security fix (issues that are related to security)
*********************************************

2008-02-10 [A] Added onlinestats plugin {GauGau}
2008-02-09 [A] Added OpenSearch plugin {GauGau}
2008-02-09 [O] Modified the code in picmgr.php to reflect security improvents imposed by Inspekt {SaWey}
2008-02-07 [C] Added nicer album drop down in modifyalb.php {SaWey}
